short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: View Roblox game analytics from RoMonitor Stats inside Roblox
short.es: Observa analiticas de juegos de Roblox desde RoMonitor Stats dentro de Roblox

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Get RoMonitor Stats right inside with the official Google Chrome extension, view Stats, Milestones and more all on the Roblox games page.

Currently RoMonitor Stats can display the following on a Roblox experience page
- General Experience Stats
- Milestones
- Name Changes
- Social Graph
